#: ../../../../../.conda/lib/python3.12/site-packages/_pytest/recwarn.py:docstring
#: of _pytest.recwarn.deprecated_call:19
msgid ""
"The return value is a list of :class:`warnings.WarningMessage` objects, one "
"for each warning emitted (regardless of whether it is an "
"``expected_warning`` or not)."
