"be able to import your namespace packages. This is best achieved by "
"installing the packages in your environment, most commonly in `\"editable\" "
"mode <https://packaging.python.org/en/latest/guides/distributing-packages-"
"using-setuptools/#working-in-development-mode>`_. If you can't install the "
"packages, consider adding the namespace root paths to :confval:`pythonpath`."
