#: ../../../doc/en/reference/reference.rst:2546
msgid "pytest testing doc"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/reference/reference.rst:2554
msgid ""
"How many sessions should pytest keep the `tmp_path` directories, according "
"to :confval:`tmp_path_retention_policy`."
